'''查理斯-曉伯特·伊坦積'''（{{lang-fr|'''Charles-Hubert Itandje'''}}，{{bd|1982年|11月2日|catIdx=Itandje, Charles}}），出生在[[法國|法國]][[波比尼|波比尼]]，是一名[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[門將|門將]]，現效力[[希超|希超]]球會[[阿特罗米托斯足球俱乐部|艾杜美圖斯]]。

== 生平 ==
=== 球會 ===
;朗斯
2001年，伊坦積在法國球會[[朗斯足球會|朗斯]]展開其足球生涯，他合共代表球會上陣了170場聯賽賽事和21場歐洲賽事<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.sitercl.com/Fichejo/I/itandjec.htm|title=Charles-Hubert Itandje|work=Le site du Racing Club de Lens|accessdate=2009-02-16|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604015552/https://www.sitercl.com/Fichejo/I/itandjec.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年[[夏天|夏天]]，朗斯購入兩名門將後，準備允許讓伊坦積離開球會加盟利物浦<ref name="Reds move">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_2651712,00.html|title=Itandje agrees Reds move|last=O'Rourke|first=Peter|date=9 August 2007|work=Sky Sports|publisher=BSkyB|accessdate=2009-02-16|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175549/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_2651712,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，會方對此說道：「朗斯的主管證實已經將伊坦積出售至利物浦，伊坦積六年的良好和忠誠的服務，我們希望他未來的生涯會好運<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.metro.co.uk/sport/football/article.html?in_article_id=60783&in_page_id=43&in_a_source=|title=Reds clinch Itandje deal|date=10 August 2007|work=Metro|publisher=Associated Newspapers Limited|accessdate=2009-02-17|archive-date=2007-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070818152638/http://www.metro.co.uk/sport/football/article.html?in_article_id=60783&in_page_id=43&in_a_source=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」

;利物浦
2007年8月，伊坦積加盟[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6938522.stm|title=Villa close in on keeper Carson|date=9 August 2007|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2009-02-16|archive-date=2021-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210704025403/https://secure-uk.imrworldwide.com/v51.js|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於[[史葛·卡臣|史葛·卡臣]]被外借至[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿土東維拉]]一整個賽季，伊坦積便作為了[[荷西·連拿|荷西·連拿]]的後備<ref name="Reds move" />。伊坦積對他的轉會該說道：「在利物浦這裡有效力達三年的好門將。我非常清楚我的加盟是作為第二門將，但是這裡有每季有60場賽事，我將會在[[英格蘭聯賽杯|聯賽杯]]和[[英格蘭足總杯|足總杯]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2669481,00.html|title=Itandje wants Reds start|last=Fraser|first=Peter|date=18 August 2007|work=Sky Sports|publisher=BSkyB|accessdate=2009-02-16|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310080048/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_2669481,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」9月25日，伊坦積在聯賽杯對[[雷丁足球會|雷丁]]的賽事中首次亮相，利物浦最終以4-2擊敗對手<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7008013.stm|title= Reading 2-4 Liverpool|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Charles_Itandje&action=edit&section=2t=McKenzie  |first=Andrew |date=25 September 2007|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=2009-02-16}}</ref>，2007/08球季，伊坦積合共上陣了3場聯賽杯賽事和4場足總杯賽事<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=27217&seasonid=137|title=Games played by Charles-Hubert Itandje in 2007/2008|work=Soccerbase|publisher=Racing Post|accessdate=2009-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203095457/http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=27217|archive-date=2009-02-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2008年[[夏天|夏天]]，利物浦買入了[[迪亞高·卡華利尼|迪亞高·卡華利尼]]後，伊坦積可供轉會至其他球隊，但被[[加拉塔沙雷體育會|加拉塔沙雷]]所拒絕<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3894881,00.html|title=Reds keeper rejects move|last=Haond|first=Patrick|date=1 August 2008|work=Sky Sports|publisher=BSkyB|accessdate=2009-02-17|archive-date=2016-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813050603/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_3894881,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伊坦積並沒有再進一步代表利物浦上陣，在2009年1月，他設法離開球會<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4857374,00.html|title=Itandje desperate to quit|last=Haond|first=Patrick|date=27 January 2009|work=SkySports|publisher=BSkyB|accessdate=2009-02-17|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310080532/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4857374,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在「紀念希斯堡事件」後伊坦積再沒有機會為利物浦披甲上陣，2009年8月被外借到[[希超|希超]]升班球隊[[卡瓦拉竞技俱乐部|卡華拉]]一整個球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/8230566.stm |title=Liverpool release Itandje on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2009-08-31 |accessdate=2010-12-09 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307032112/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/8230566.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣19場。2010/11年球季伊坦積返回利物浦，其合約在球季結束後屆滿，於隊中淪為五號門將，甚至沒有官方的大合照中出現。

;艾杜美圖斯
2010年12月8日[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]宣佈棄用伊坦積，讓他可於冬季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]重開免費加盟[[希超|希超]]球會[[阿特罗米托斯足球俱乐部|艾杜美圖斯]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/9269899.stm |title=Keeper Charles Itandje quits Liverpool for Atromitos |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-08 |accessdate=2010-12-09 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126103432/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/9269899.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 紀念希斯堡事件 ====
2009年4月，在[[希斯堡慘劇|希斯堡慘劇]]二十週年紀念追悼會後，伊坦積被投訴指他在追悼會上一直笑著和行為不當<ref name="Hillsborough-guardian">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2009/apr/17/charles-itandje-hillsborough-service-liverpool|title=Liverpool to offload Charles Itandje after his Hillsborough service antics|publisher=''The Guardian''|date=2009-04-17|accessdate=2009-04-17|archive-date=2012-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009055438/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2009/apr/17/charles-itandje-hillsborough-service-liverpool|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伊坦積的行為受到了利物浦的譴責，他們將設法施加最高刑罰<ref name="Hillsborough-guardian" />。最後，伊坦積對他的行為向悲痛的死傷者家屬和利物浦球迷道歉，並且被球會停賽14天<ref name="Memorial service player 'sorry'">{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/merseyside/8006204.stm|title=Memorial service player 'sorry'|date=18 April 2009|work=BBC News|accessdate=2009-05-19|archive-date=2009-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090421050824/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/merseyside/8006204.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 國家隊 ===
雖然伊坦積的父母來自[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]，但在[[法國|法國]]出生及擁有[[公民|公民]]資格的伊坦積選擇代表[[法國21歲以下國家足球隊|法國U21]]參賽<ref name="LFCTV">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/team/squad/itandje/|title=1st team squad profiles: Charles Itandje|work=Liverpool Football Club official website|accessdate=2009-02-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090212172912/http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/team/squad/itandje/|archivedate=2009-02-12}}</ref>。2006年，伊坦積曾被[[法國國家足球隊|法國]]徵召作預選<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.rlfoot.fr/index.php?page=http://www.rlfoot.fr/Selections/07-08_A_joueurs.htm List of the pre-selected players in the French A-squad in the season 2007-2008] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rlfoot.fr/index.php?page=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rlfoot.fr%2FSelections%2F07-08_A_joueurs.htm |date=20180214014617 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11682_2374911,00.html|title=Itandje eyes France chance|last=Haond|first=Patrick|date=26 April 2006|work=SkySports|publisher=BSkyB|accessdate=2009-02-17|archive-date=2017-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170413070702/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11682_2374911,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伊坦積被選入[[法國21歲以下國家足球隊|法國U21]]，並憑籍他在[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]時干擾對手的舞蹈而為人認識。

2010年伊坦積表示希望代表[[喀麥隆國家足球隊|喀麥隆]]參加國際賽，於10月獲[[國際足協|國際足協]]澄清准許<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.afrikansoccer.com/2010/10/fifa-clears-liverpool-gaolie-itandje-to-play-for-cameroon/ |title=Fifa clears Liverpool gaolie Itandje to play for Cameroon |publisher=''afrikansoccer.com'' |date=2010-10-15 |accessdate=2010-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101017054120/http://www.afrikansoccer.com/2010/10/fifa-clears-liverpool-gaolie-itandje-to-play-for-cameroon/ |archivedate=2010-10-17 }}</ref>。

